page.title: 12MUSIC
page.content: THERE ARE 10 STRINGED INSTRUMENTS THE LUTE,VIOLIN,BANJO,UKULELE,MANDOLIN,THE CLASSICAL GUITAR,BASS,HARP,VIOLA AND CELLO.THERE ARE10 WOODWIND INSTRUMENTS THE OBOE,ENGLISH HORN, CLARINET, BASS CLARINET, FLUTE, PICCOLO, BASS SAXOPHONE, SOPRANO SAXOPHONE, TENOR SAXOPHONE, BARITONE SAXOPHONE.THERE ARE 7 BRASS INSTRUMENTS THE TRUMPET, BUGLE,TROMBONE, FRENCH HORN, SOUSAPHONE, BARITONE AND FLUGEL HORN. THERE ARE 10 PERCUSSION INSTRUMENTS THE KETTLE DRUM,SNARE DRUM BONGO DRUM,BASS DRUM,VIBRAPHONE,TRIANGLE CYMBLES,SLEIGHBELLS,CHIMES AND THE GONG.THERE ARE 3 KEYBOARD INSTRUMENTS THEY ARE THE PIANO,HARPSICHORD AND THE PIPE ORGAN.THERE ARE OTHER INSTRUMENTS THE ACCORDION,HARMONICA, BAGPIPES AND RECORDERS.
